TopicTitle: Joysticks Controllers "Not Found" can not map axis

Articles.Content:
I am using the latest KSP windows 32 bit build 1.0.5.1028 (WindowsPlayer)

 

Unable to map a Thrustmaster Warthog combined with TARGET profile to any axis.  In the axis detection the controller/axis is always detected (see first screen) but once I click Accept there is a message "Not Found"

http://imgur.com/xEVdjmx

http://imgur.com/QVrQLqW

 

This profile used to work in older KSP.  ALSO I have Simped Vario Pro rudder pedals, that experience the same thing.  Clean install, deleted settings.cfg and retried 1 axis, FAIL.

Please fix this bug, KSP is unusable for me for the first time in years.
